data.name: basicInstrTxtBox.Text
data.value:
1) Select the game you want and click the "Install" button. 2) If its the first time you're installing a server, select the installation folder, and then wait for the installation to finish. 3) Type "quit" in the command line after the installation has finished.(only for steam servers) 4) Configure the server the way you like by editing the settings files (optional). 5) Start the server and enjoy!
NOTE: If you need extra help, some servers include a guide in the "Extra" section. You can also go to the "Help-Language" tab for additional help. You can also join our group on steam and ask for help about your issue.
